---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us" description="Instru-Met Corporation has served customers for over 50 years.">
  <div class="container py-16 lg:py-20">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-3">About</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">About Instru-Met</h1>
    <div class="prose-body mt-8 max-w-prose space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-foreground/90">
      <p>
        Instru-Met Corporation is a strength of materials test equipment company
        and a classic tensile tester expert. We have served customers for over
        50 years, working with manufacturers, testing labs, universities,
        companies, and entrepreneurs across the United States, Mexico, Canada,
        Hungary, and Europe.
      </p>
      <p>
        We repair and calibrate every tensile tester on the market and have
        dismantled and examined countless machines. That experience informs how
        we rebuild, retrofit, and build our own tensile testing machines:
        mechanically, electrically, and operationally.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
